workflow: GlyphLockUnfold
intent: unfold a GE² envelope — verify TOTP, decrypt AEAD, decompress, glyph decode, verify merkle root
step 1: read glyphpack manifest → manifest
step 2: generate current TOTP code → totp_code
step 3: verify TOTP within time window → totp_verified
step 4: AEAD decrypt ciphertext with payload key → compressed
step 5: deflate decompress → glyph_encoded
step 6: glyph decode with reverse dictionary → raw_file
step 7: verify SHA256 merkle root → merkle_verified
step 8: issue unfold receipt → unfold_receipt
artifact: unfold_receipt
receipt: SHA256 chained — unfold proof with TOTP verification
value: file reconstructed only with correct decoder, time key, and policy
